                        <div class="container-shape-help">
                            <div class='object-container'>
                                <div class="circle"></div>
                                <div class="label" data-lang='en'>Objects</div>
                                <div class="label" data-lang='cat'>1Objects</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class='object-container'>
                                <div class="square"></div>
                                <div class="label" data-lang='en'>Data sources</div>
                                <div class="label" data-lang='cat'>1Data sources</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class='object-container'>
                                <div class="triangle"></div>
                                <div class="label" data-lang='en'>Purposes</div>
                                <div class="label" data-lang='cat'>1Purposes</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p data-lang='en'>Touch and select objects and link them with data and purposes. Every object unfolds a selection of related projects to inspire you about how connectivity can enhance people's lives.</p>
