                    <hr/>
                    <div class="credits-container">
                        <div class="credits" data-lang='en'>
                            <p>Creative Direction and production by <span class='credit-bold'>Alpha Ville (Estela Oliva & Carmen Sales Pino)</span><br>
                            Technology & Development by <span class='credit-bold'>FLUUUID (Silvio Paganini & William Mapan)</span><br>
